div.div: Commented on#35599 Modal "hidden" event is firing while the modal is still visible

@kc-jeffk everything is working as it should . When the event you are using is triggered, first the function passed in the event listener is executed then the actual process is executed . So when the modal close event is triggered your alert function is executed first the the modal close function is triggered .
